00:00:02.830 --> 00:00:09.509
Jehovah is the only true God, the sovereign of the universe.

00:00:09.509 --> 00:00:15.949
Some wicked spirits and even humans have deceitfully pretended to be gods.

00:00:15.949 --> 00:00:21.109
